comment: McCallum (SAC) makes body to body contact with Harden (HOU).
Prigioni (HOU) makes contact with McCallum's (SAC) leg and body and the contact affects his movement to the basket.
Casspi (SAC) makes contact with Prigioni's (HOU) arm and affects his ability to pass.
Ariza (HOU) makes contact with Thompson's (SAC) arm and the contact affects his movement to the basket and layup attempt.
Cousins (SAC) jumps vertically and legally contests Jones' (HOU) play to the basket.
Ariza (HOU) cleanly knocks the ball away from McLemore (SAC).
LHH and RATR shows McLemore (SAC) steps OOB after recovering the loose ball.
Harden (HOU) dislodges Cousins (SAC) from behind during rebounding.
Thompson (SAC) commits a take foul on Harden (HOU).
Cousins (SAC) and Ariza (HOU) make incidental contact on the perimeter.
LATR shows that Cousins (SAC) initiates the contact with Jones (HOU) who maintains legal guarding position as he defends the driving layup attempt.
